      "title": "Standard distance in univariate and multivariate analysis",
      "abstract": "Abstract We propose to use the term standard distance for the quantity in univariate analysis and show that it can be easily generalized to the multivariate situation, where it coincides with the square root of the Mahalanobis distance between two samples."
